Retrieve a bucket (for read api)
GET /backdrop/bucket?data_group=<data_group>&data_type=<data_type>

Retrieve a bucket (for write api)
GET /backdrop/bucket/<name>

{
  "name": "licensing_application",
  "data_group": "licensing",
  "data_type": "application",
  "bearer_token": "my-bearer-token",
  "capped_size": null,
  "realtime": false,
  "auto_ids": null,
  "upload_format": null,
  "upload_filters": [],
  "queryable": true,
  "raw_queries_allowed": false
}


Retrieve a user
GET /backdrop/user/<email>

{
  "email": "foo@bar.com",
  "buckets": ["foo", "bar"]
}
